comments.body:
@vmari  was at least active when merging  https://github.com/vmari/DotEnv.jl/pull/9 so not completely MIA. I just think it is unfortunate to merge this package, and then if @vmari answers in a week it will be deprecated.

Are you in a hurry to get this registered? It does not seem like a package you would have other packages depend on and thus can just add by URL for the time being?

We don't have a formal process for things like this yet, see https://github.com/JuliaRegistries/General/issues/25367 for example.
